sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Chain as Base contract logs
  participant Watcher as Event watcher
  participant Cursor as Durable cursor
  participant Decoder as Event decoder
  participant Store as Brain DB
  participant Recon as Reconciliation job
  participant Dash as Readiness dashboard
  participant DLQ as Dead letter

  Watcher->>Cursor: Load last confirmed block per contract
  Watcher->>Chain: Fetch logs after cursor with confirmation depth
  Chain-->>Watcher: Logs by block and tx
  loop each log
    Watcher->>Decoder: Decode by contract ABI and topic
    alt decoded and canonical
      Decoder->>Store: Upsert by chain_id, contract, tx_hash, log_index
      Store->>Recon: Correlate to PaymentIntent, proof, policy, agent, or escrow state
      Recon->>Dash: Update lag, health, and correlation metrics
    else decode failed or unexpected
      Decoder->>DLQ: Record raw log, block, tx, topic, error
      DLQ->>Dash: Increment dead-letter metric
    end
  end
  Watcher->>Cursor: Advance only after durable writes
  alt reorg detected
    Watcher->>Store: Mark affected derived rows uncertain
    Watcher->>Cursor: Rewind to safe block
    Watcher->>Chain: Replay canonical logs
  end
